sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant ApplicationController
    participant HMRC_Auth as HMRC Auth
    participant MongoDB as MongoDB (agent-application)

    Client->>ApplicationController: GET /application
    ApplicationController->>HMRC_Auth: Authenticate (GG, Agent affinity, User/Admin roles)
    alt Auth fails or HMRC-AS-AGENT active or Assistant role
        HMRC_Auth-->>ApplicationController: 401 Unauthorised
        ApplicationController-->>Client: 401 Unauthorised
    else Auth succeeds
        HMRC_Auth-->>ApplicationController: internalUserId
        ApplicationController->>MongoDB: findOne(internalUserId)
        alt Record found
            MongoDB-->>ApplicationController: AgentApplication
            ApplicationController-->>Client: 200 OK (AgentApplication JSON)
        else Record not found
            MongoDB-->>ApplicationController: None
            ApplicationController-->>Client: 204 No Content
        end
    end
